<h2><b><u>WAYS TO REDUCE SOCIAL MEDIA ADDICTION</u></b></h2>
<ol>
<li>Turn off Notifications</li>
<li>Keep your phone away as much as possible</li>
<li>Start having alternatehobbies like reading,gardening etc</li>
<li>Go for a digital detox</li>
</ol>
